title: Miranda (2009) All Episodes, Complete Series 1-3
description:
Miranda is 6 feet 1 inch tall and gets called 'Sir' once too often. She has never fit in with her old boarding school friends and finds social situations awkward, especially around men.

In this awesome package, we have included all three series of Miranda and the two special finale episodes in an easily navigable format. No files with incredibly confusing names such as .miranda.2009.s1.e1.dog.avi. Instead we have files named as so; Miranda - S01E01 (Dog).avi.

Files:
- Series 1: Episode 1-6
- Series 2: Episode 1-6
- Series 3: Episode 1-6 + 2 Finale Special Episodes

PLEASE ALWAYS SEED TO SUPPORT US AND HELP OTHERS! THANK YOU FOR DOWNLOADING!
